        "Completely relaxed and unaware of any threat",
        "Relaxed but faintly attentive to a nearby presence",
        "Mildly cautious while maintaining polite composure",
        "Reserved and keeping a modest distance",
        "Politely asking for space and discouraging further approach",
        "Clearly stating discomfort and requesting to stop",
        "Actively avoiding being alone and staying near safer surroundings",
        "Refusing proximity and maintaining distance",
